          </p>

          <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h4 class="card-title fw-bold mb-4">Experience Highlights</h4>
                  <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
